quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  60,1,"Eehey mon goon…óin…ìe wote njaggire a√±…ìe Mi e a√±…ìe mon heet…ìe ho…óon mberlo e mum en gilli te ko…ìe yeddu…ìe goongo gar…óo o e mon, ho…ìe njaltina nelaa…óo e onon sabu tan on ngoon…óanii Alla joomi mon, tawde on njalti sabu jihaadi e laawol Am e …óa…ìjude weluya am, ho…óon cuurtana…ìe kabaruuji juul…ìe ngam …ìe mbele mon, Mbe…óa anndi ko cuu…óoton e ko …ìanngi…óon, kala e mon ba…ó…óo …óuum o majji laawol peewngol"
  60,2,Si…ìe peewnatiima e mon …ìe ngOnana mon a√±…ìe …ìe mberta juu…óe ma…ì…ìe e …óem…óe mum en e mbaadi mbonndi …ìe nji…óiina nde ngonaton heeferee…ìe
  60,3,Nafatah on en…óameeje mon wonah …ìi…ì…ìe mon √±ande darnga O seernda hakkunde mon Alla na yi*a ko golloton ko
  60,4,"Woodanii on √±eemtinirde mo∆¥∆¥ere e Ibraahiima e …ìeen wondu…ìe e mum nde …ìe mbi*i pellet ko min his…ìe e mon e ko ndewaton ko wonah Alla ko, min njeddii on fee√±i hakkunde men nga√±ngu e tikkere haa pooma haa ngoon…óinon Alla gooto O, si wonah konngol Ibraahiima wonande baaba makko pellet ma mi yaafnano ma, mi alanaama hay huunde ka Alla, joomi amen min mbakkaliima e Ma ko e Ma min ndutti e ko e Ma woni wattande"
  60,5,"joomi amen wota wa…ó min fitina wonande …ìeen yeddu…ìe, yaafa amen joomi amen pellet ko aan woni teddu…óo mbo fooletaake √±ee√±…óu…óo"
  60,6,"Woodaniina mon e ma…ì…ìe √±eemtanirgal mo∆¥∆¥al wonande oon joortii…óo e Alla e √±alngu laakara, oon …óuurnii…óo noon Pellet Alla ko gala jettaa…óo"